index_terms: SEATTLE KING COUNTY DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC HEALTH
summary: An Ordinance amending Section 2 of Ordinance No. 26759, entitled "An Ordinance authorizing the Commissioner of Health to appoint a General Superintendent of the Garbage Collection and destruction division of the Department of Health and Sanitation of the City of Seattle, and fixing the salary thereof," approved March 18, 1911, by reducing the salary provided for in said section.
